sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant REST as REST Handler
    participant Auth as Auth Middleware
    participant UC as TaskUseCase
    participant Domain as Task Entity
    participant UserRepo as User Repository
    participant LabelRepo as Label Repository
    participant TaskRepo as Task Repository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Event as Event Publisher
    participant Kafka as Kafka

    Client->>Auth: POST /api/v1/tasks
    Auth->>REST: authenticated request context
    REST->>UC: CreateTask(ctx, input)
    UC->>UC: validate DTO and parse priority
    UC->>Domain: NewTask(title, description, priority, creatorID)
    Domain-->>UC: task entity

    alt assignee provided
        UC->>UserRepo: ExistsByID(ctx, assigneeID)
        UserRepo->>DB: SELECT user existence
        DB-->>UserRepo: result
        UserRepo-->>UC: exists or not
    end

    loop each label ID
        UC->>LabelRepo: ExistsByID(ctx, labelID)
        LabelRepo->>DB: SELECT label existence
        DB-->>LabelRepo: result
        LabelRepo-->>UC: exists or not
    end

    UC->>TaskRepo: Save(ctx, task)
    TaskRepo->>DB: INSERT task and label relations
    DB-->>TaskRepo: success
    TaskRepo-->>UC: success

    UC->>Event: Publish(task created event)
    Event->>Kafka: produce message if configured
    Kafka-->>Event: ack or error

    UC-->>REST: task output DTO
    REST-->>Client: 201 Created
